{"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"href":"/posts/wordle-solver/"}}},"blocks":[{"key":"ws2intro","text":"Let's dive into two key game-changers:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h1","text":"Embracing Letter Frequencies:","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p1","text":"Unveiling the Uneven Alphabet: The 26 letters in the English language aren't evenly distributed across words. Some letters, like S, E, A, R, and O, reign supreme in usage.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p2","text":"Harnessing High-Frequency Starters: By strategically choosing your first guess to include these heavy hitters, you can maximize information gain. For instance, \"AROSE\" covers a whopping 95% of words in the 5-letter dictionary, exponentially increasing your chances of early letter discovery.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p3","text":"Adapting to the Narrowing Wordscape: As the game progresses, continue to consider letter frequencies within the remaining possible words. This statistical approach guides you towards guesses that efficiently reveal the hidden word.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h2","text":"Delving into the Untapped:","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p4","text":"Second-Guess Surprises: While logic might suggest choosing a word from the possible solutions list, consider the power of the unexpected. A second guess composed entirely of unused letters can often unveil more letters than a seemingly logical choice.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p5","text":"Expanding Your Letter Arsenal: By embracing words like \"UNITY\" after \"AROSE,\" you cover 100% of letters in the 5-letter dictionary, ensuring a comprehensive exploration of possibilities.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p6","text":"Remember: Wordle is a game of both logic and creativity. By understanding letter frequencies and embracing unconventional guesses, you'll unlock a winning strategy that blends statistical prowess with linguistic intuition.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h3","text":"Conclusion","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p7","text":"By integrating these strategies, you'll elevate your Wordle game to new heights, conquering each daily puzzle with confidence and finesse.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2link","text":"Check out the original post","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":27,"key":0}],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h4","text":"Game Board","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2p8","text":"Update the board below so it matches your current game. Mark each letter as a near miss (🟨) or a hit (🟩).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h5","text":"Letter frequency in the dictionary","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h6","text":"Suggested Solutions","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ws2h7","text":"Words made of untried letters","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
